folder: Amboy Road & Arden Avenue, Staten Island, NY
text:
Amboy Road, at the N.E. corner of Arden Ave.
May 4, 1926.
P. L. Sperr.

folder: Arden Avenue & Amboy Road, Staten Island, NY
text:
Arden Ave. (directly behind house, telephone poles thereon), adjoining the N.E. corner of Amboy Road, showing the Bovaniser house occupying that site. The house belonged to J. Dempsey in 1874
(Beers' map). The view is northwestward.
April 30, 1933.
P. L. Sperr.
